<a:Warden:849839123988873216> The latest Java <:java:598000584691417098> Snapshot is here, and to help support our players we will be, again, using the Beta Feedback category and the channels within to capture player feedback for the game development team. 

Java Snapshot Changelog: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/minecraft-snapshot-22w15a

The feedback channels will be open for a limited time for you all to submit your feedback and then will be closed so that the team has enough time to collect it all. 

Wanting to participate? You'll need a specific role to access and post in these channels as well as have the snapshot downloaded/enabled. 

To participate in Java Snapshots: Snapshots are available for Minecraft: Java Edition. To install the snapshot, open up the Minecraft Launcher (https://www.minecraft.net/download.html) and enable snapshots in the "Installations" tab.

To opt-in to the beta feedback: <#943439493120262155>

**Minecraft: Java Edition - Snapshot 22w15a**
https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/minecraft-snapshot-22w15a

**New Additions**
<:warden:763094083785850911> Added new ranged attack for Wardens
🏆 Added new Advancements

**Changes**
🏞️ The main menu background now shows a Wild Update panorama
<:allay_face:951407387049353246> Allays have a natural health regen of 2 health per second
🎵 A previous change to Noteblocks that only Wool and Wool Carpets would block the sounds has been reverted
🍀 Moss Carpet generates on top of Mangrove Tree’s roots
🌳 Tall Mangroves are far more common than Short Mangroves in Mangrove Swamps
👃 The vertical range Wardens get angry at a target while sniffing is now 20 blocks instead of 6 blocks
🔊 Carpets, like Wool blocks, can now dampen the vibrations

**Fixes**
🖼️ Item frames/Glow item frames don't change their hitbox if they contain a map
🛏️ Sleeping in a custom dimension with "natural" set to false causes crash
✨ sculk_charge cannot be used in /particle command
🌃 Darkness pulsing option is not saved
<:allay:951406311323607080> Allay can be pushed around with {NoAI:1b}
🌳 Mangrove roots sometimes don't generate waterlogged when generating within water
⛵ You can't open the boat with chests without a shift, even when you can't get into the boat
<:warden:763094083785850911> Warden can forget a target it just roared at
🖌️ Inconsistent shading in boat item sprites
📡 Powering a beacon disconnects player from server
📳 Activated sculk shriekers fail to summon the warden when broken
🧭 You can use a Recovery Compass on a Lodestone
🌚 The Darkness effect is not required for the "How Did We Get Here?" advancement

...And many more!

**Minecraft: Bedrock Edition - Beta & Preview 1.19.0.24/25**
https://feedback.minecraft.net/hc/en-us/articles/5540500564365

**Known Issues/Notices**
<:xbox:628987335731576855> Xbox Series X|S players may receive an error message (code 0x8b050033) when launching Minecraft Preview. Uninstall and reinstall Minecraft Preview to complete the update and resolve the error.
📦 Interactive blocks (such as Hoppers) cannot be shift-placed continuously without opening the UI
👁️ Spectator Mode was accidentally made available in the previous beta, and is not finished. It will be moved to Experimental Toggles in upcoming betas, and all bug reports about Spectator Mode will __**not**__ be accepted

**New Additions**
🧭  Added Recovery Compass & Echo Shards

**Removed Features**
📯 Removed Copper Horn

**Vanilla Parity**
🏞️ Several improvements to level chunk blending

**Changes & Fixes**
🛥️ Player can now change hotbar item slot while in a Boat
🐸 Froglight and Frogspawn blocks now have new sounds
🗜️ Reinforced Deepslate can no longer be pushed by Pistons
<:warden:763094083785850911> Warden now has a hurt animation when taking damage
🌚 Spawning a Warden in Creative mode no longer applies the Darkness effect to the player
🏃 Running away from a Sculk Shrieker during shrieking is no longer a viable way of preventing the summoning of a Warden
<:redstone_dust:691841117012099164> Sculk Shriekers should not be triggered by Redstone activation
💢 Warden will now prioritize players over mobs when angry
📯 Added Goat Horn variations to the Pillager outposts
<:allay:951406311323607080> The Allay now regenerates two health each second
✨ Fixed enchantment option on Pocket UI Profile not being displayed

...And more!

A new Bedrock Beta/Preview is now available, with a Recovery Compass and Echo Shards, and various other bug fixes and tweaks to existing content. To help support our players we will be, again, using the Beta Feedback category and the channels within to capture player feedback for the game development team. 

Bedrock Beta Changelog: https://aka.ms/MinecraftBeta

The feedback channels will be open for a limited time for you all to submit your feedback and then will be closed so that the team has enough time to collect it all. 

Wanting to participate? You'll need a specific role to access and post in these channels as well as have the beta downloaded/enabled. 

To download the beta: https://aka.ms/JoinMCBeta

To opt-in to the beta feedback: <#943439493120262155>
